2006-09-20  Edward Hervey  <edward@fluendo.com>

	* ext/ffmpeg/gstffmpegcodecmap.c: (gst_ffmpeg_codecid_to_caps),
	(gst_ffmpeg_caps_to_codecid), (gst_ffmpeg_get_codecid_longname):
