2006-04-08  Wim Taymans  <wim@fluendo.com>

	* ext/ffmpeg/gstffmpegdec.c: (gst_ffmpegdec_class_init),
	(gst_ffmpegdec_init), (gst_ffmpegdec_finalize),
	(gst_ffmpegdec_query), (gst_ffmpegdec_update_qos),
