	  we have better ways of debugging caps
	* ext/ffmpeg/gstffmpegenc.c: (gst_ffmpegenc_setcaps):
	  ye gods.  get_template_caps doesn't return a ref, so when the
	  pad was not linked, crashes would ensue.  Serves me right.

