	* Update for state change type and macro changes.

2005-08-19  Wim Taymans  <wim@fluendo.com>

	* ext/ffmpeg/gstffmpegenc.c: (gst_ffmpegenc_setcaps),
	(gst_ffmpegenc_chain_video), (gst_ffmpegenc_change_state):
